# Auto Key Presser

## Instructions

* Unzip before use
* Run the .exe file
* Press **P** to start/stop auto pressing
* Press **ESC** to exit

## Settings

* Default key: **X**
* You can change key and interval in the app

## Notes

* This tool is made for AFK use
* Some games may block simulated input
* If your account gets banned, use at your own risk

## Warning

* Some antivirus software may flag this as a virus (false positive)
* This is normal for self-made tools

